<font color="#FF0000">VIETNAM MOVIES.</font><br>
<tt>Tue Jun 17 13:36:47 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Things that contributed to differing personal views of the VN War<br>
1.  Four war zones (I, II, III, IV Corps)<br>
2.  Five types of terrain: mountains, forests, triple canopy jungle, elephant grass and lots of water.<br>
3.  Only one year tours out of 26 years of involvement (1959-1975)<br>
4.  Differing unit assignments and equipment.<br>
5.  Individual backgrounds and social experiences.<br>
6.  Average age of GI in 'Nam is 19.  WWII: 25 Korea:28<br><br>
E-mail me for expansion of above.
